======


A case distinction.

Content across different branches can be aligned with the `&` symbol.

# Example
```typ
$ f(x, y) := cases(
  1 "if" (x dot y)/2 <= 0,
  2 "if" x "is even",
  3 "if" x in NN,
  4 "else",
) $
```


